{"messageId": "1516ef0166af2890", "headers": {"From": "Ben Goertzel <ben@goertzel.org>", "Date": "Fri, 4 Dec 2015 22:40:05 +0100", "Subject": "Re: [opencog-dev] Re: More PLN book questions and errata"}, "body": "Yeah, Hruy in Ethiopia did that conversion for me. Just do not tell the publisher of the print version."},
{"messageId": "1516ef11795663e4", "headers": {"From": "Ben Goertzel <ben@goertzel.org>", "Date": "Fri, 4 Dec 2015 22:41:11 +0100", "Subject": "Re: [opencog-dev] More PLN book questions and errata"}, "body": "Fortunately for me, your hard questions are all about Matt's work, not mine."},
